# This project reads no environment variables.
#
# LLM credentials: the code authenticates to Google Cloud Vertex AI with a
# GCP service-account key file located at ./service-account.json
# (path set by SERVICE_ACCOUNT_PATH in config.py, region by GCP_REGION).
# Place your own key file there; it is never committed. It must contain a
# valid "project_id" and grant the Vertex AI User role, e.g.:
#
#   service-account.json  ->  {"type": "service_account",
#                              "project_id": "your-gcp-project-id", ...}
#
# No other secrets are required. g++ and the APPS dataset are the only
# additional runtime dependencies (see README.md).
